<fr:li>for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B_{1},B_{2}\in \mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex>, for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  X]]></fr:tex>, if <fr:tex
